# =============================================================================
# FORGE SOLOMON — runtime config TEMPLATE (.env.example)
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. This is a template only. The REAL file next to it is  solomon.env
#   2. Copy this file:  cp solomon.env.example solomon.env  then edit values.
#   3. Redeploy (push.sh) so the box reloads.
#
# Solomon is the daycare's HEAD AGENT — a 30-year executive director. He reads
# the whole center (ops, billing, enrollment, growth, connected systems + the
# business brief), writes a prioritized operating brief, owns enrollment, and
# routes work to the role sub-agents you add under him. He never takes an
# outward action on his own — every SMS / invoice / ad launch stays your one-tap
# approval. His only autonomous writes are his own brain playbook + bus notes.
#
# SAFETY:
#   This folder is a SIBLING of the web app ("forge rei/"), so it lives OUTSIDE
#   the web-served dir. Nothing here is reachable over HTTP. Keys stay private.
# =============================================================================

# --- Cadence -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Hours between Solomon's autonomous operating-brief refreshes on the box.
FORGE_SOLOMON_BRIEF_EVERY_H=6

# --- Self-improvement --------------------------------------------------------
# Briefs Solomon must produce before an auto self-improve fires.
FORGE_SOLOMON_LEARN_EVERY=8
# Minimum minutes between self-improvement writes (rate guard).
FORGE_SOLOMON_LEARN_GAP_MIN=45

# --- Anthropic (Solomon's OWN Claude key) ------------------------------------
# Optional. Solomon's dedicated key. If unset he FALLS BACK to the shared
# agency/wholesale Anthropic key, so he works before his own key is set.
# SOLOMON_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Obsidian brain (vault) --------------------------------------------------
# Optional override for the Agentic-OS Obsidian vault path. Solomon reads his
# learned playbook from <vault>/Skills/solomon-playbook.md in addition to the
# local skills/solomon-playbook.md in this folder.
# FORGE_VAULT=/Users/yg4st/Desktop/Agentic-OS/vault
